cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about deep learning algorithms for salient object detection, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel module for modeling contrast via intra-channel and inter-channel correlations, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also focuses on achieving high inference efficiency, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed algorithm on various datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
